{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483950/extras/UnderPressure_StoreGif_1c.gif?t=1710079068\" /><br><br>In the abyss, the Diver meets the Kraken! To survive he will have to reach the surface!<br><br>Each card represents a progression stage, from the abyss #0 to the surface #42.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483950/extras/UnderPressure_StoreGif_2c.gif?t=1710079068\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Goals:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Diver wants to reach the surface, he starts from card #0 and can step up to 3 stages max per turn<br></li><li>  Kraken wants to catch him by guessing all he's played cards. Kraken can guess up to 3 cards per turn.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483950/extras/UnderPressure_StoreGif_3c.gif?t=1710079068\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Diver can use boosts by sacrificing a card. It can extend step by +2 per sacrificed card! It can be used to play far cards or to trick Kraken!<br></li><li>  Kraken can guess multiple cards each turn, but if one is wrong, guess is failed! It helps to catch Diver faster but might be risky!</li></ul><br>Cards are distributed in three decks according to their value: 1-14, 15-28, 29-41.<br>Pick wisely and you may win the game!<br><br>Under Pressure is and adaptation of Tim Fowers's card game &quot;Fugitive&quot;.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2483950?t=1710079068","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483950/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1710079068","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483950/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1710079068","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483950/capsule_184x6